                            <comment id="13694638" author="ay" created="Thu, 27 Jun 2013 11:41:06 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi Dennis,&lt;br/&gt;
yes. This retrieval thing works because of what WrappedMessageContext&apos;s handling of jaxws attarchents retrieval at its getter method, which dynamically creates the jaxws&apos;s attachment-map out of the cxf&apos;s attachment-set, which Dan mentioned in the mail thread.&lt;/p&gt;

